Class FieldLabelResolver

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, polyglot.util.Copy<polyglot.visit.NodeVisitor>

    public class FieldLabelResolver
extends polyglot.visit.ContextVisitor
    A visitor used to resolving field labels. We want to resolve field labels of all the classes before the label checking pass, because these field labels might be included in other labels, and thus need to be resolved first. This visitor also adds dependencies so that the label checking pass for this job will not run until the FieldLabelResolver for all jobs it is dependent on has run.
